          <br /><br />
          I'm passionate about crafting intuitive interfaces, optimizing performance, and continuously learning new technologies to bring ideas to life on the web. Whether it's a landing page, full-stack project, or a custom component â€” I love turning concepts into real, functional digital experiences.
        </p>
        <a 
          href="/SANTHOSH_Resume.pdf" 
          download 
          class="inline-block mt-4 px-6 py-3 bg-[#FF9143] hover:bg-[#AB6432] text-white font-semibold rounded-lg shadow transition duration-300"
